Package jtorrent.protocols.bittorrent.thp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    THPRemote
    Interface defining the available remote methods for a RMI announce handler.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnounceHandler
    Handles Announce messages from socket connections for a container using the simpleframework.http library for handling http messages on the URL http://ip:port/announce of the tracker server.
    AnnounceHandlerRMI
    RMI implementation for Tracker server to handle announce requests from clients.
    AnnounceRMIServer
    Server to host RMI announce handler of a tracker.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Event
    Events that are possible in an announce message.
